service: analytics-tracker

useDotenv: true

plugins:
  - serverless-offline

custom:
  serverless-offline:
    httpPort: 4001  # Different port from your main backend (4000)
    noPrependStageInUrl: true

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs24.x
  stage: ${opt:stage, 'dev'}
  region: us-east-1
  environment:
    # These will be overridden by your .env file
    ALLOWED_BUCKETS: ${env:ALLOWED_BUCKETS}
    CORS_ORIGIN: ${env:CORS_ORIGIN, '*'}

functions:
  track:
    handler: lambda/index.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: track
          method: post
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: track
          method: options
          cors: true
